Class LabelType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.primaresearch.clc.phd.ontology.label.LabelType

    public class LabelType
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.gwt.user.client.rpc.IsSerializable
    Ontology label type. A type can be abstract (super type for one or more sub-types; equivalent to 'concept'/'class') or it can be concrete (no sub-types; equivalent to 'individual'/'instance').

    clc
